T Pumpy: This is your golden chance of becoming a landlord in Abuja A recent survey by Human Development Index (HDI) ranked Abuja, Nigeria’s capital as one of the fast developing cities in Africa. With this, T Pumpy Concept Limited, developers of T Pumpy Estate in Abuja is giving Nigerians the chance of becoming a landlord in the emerging African Mega City. For over the years, the real estate company has continued to carve a niche for itself by offering affordable and reliable services. The company has been in existence since 2009, and it’s totally committed to making its utmost contribution in the development process of our environment in the aforementioned area, for the betterment of all Nigerians. We aim to be a globally recognized, preferred and respectable property developer in Nigeria. With 22 housing estates spread across the nation’s powerhouse,’ T-Pumpy Concept has a corporate vision, which “is to be the most sought for and estate developer in Nigeria. To be the leading real estate development company that will provide the highest number of decent, accessible, comfortable and affordable houses while achieving global housing standard.” Determined to make houses and land affordable for every Nigerian, the emerging face of real estate business, had in January announced a slash in its 4/5 bedroom duplex land sales with massive discounts. According to the CEO, Tayo Adaralegebe, the land is about 650sqm for 4 or 5 bedroom duplex or penthouse or can be used for 4-bedroom standard bungalow. Explaining in detail the new development, Mr, Adaralegebe said the market value of the land if N3m, however, the company is giving out 20 percent discount, which is N600,000 and 2,020 block, which is valued at N380,000. “Total value discount is N980,000 off 3,000,000 which is 2,020,000. Pay 2,020,000 the land is yours.” The promo, which started on January 1, 2020 is expected to end on March 31, 2020. This is your golden chance of owning a land/house in Abuja. Visit us today at o